  ## 摘要
  
  Kashier integration enables secure, local payment processing for Egyptian businesses by exposing REST APIs to create payment orders, present hosted checkout pages or iFrame flows, verify transactions, manage refunds, and receive asynchronous webhook notifications. Use it to accept EGP and multi-currency payments (USD, GBP, EUR) from credit/debit cards, mobile wallets, and bank installment plans in e-commerce, SaaS, marketplaces, and billing systems. Key features include API key and HMAC-SHA256 signature-based authentication, sandbox and production base URLs, environment-variable credential storage, and endpoints for reconciliation and refund handling. Core advantages are simplified PCI scope via hosted/iframe options, real-time webhook-driven status updates, robust security with request signing, and separate test/live keys for safe development and smooth go-live migration.
  
