  ### Payment Initialization (Order Hash Generation) [Permalink for this section](https://lobehub.com/zh/skills/africandigitalassetframework-africa-stack-skills-kashier\#payment-initialization-order-hash-generation)
  
  Before initiating any payment, generate an order hash using HMAC-SHA256. This validates the order data and prevents tampering.
  
  **Order Hash Generation:**
  
  **Request Body (backend):**
  
